g and pThumb installed and if not, you can download and install those dependencies under the&nbsp;dependencies&nbsp;tab.</li><li>After that it will add the needed ClientConfig settings, BlogIt chunks, plugins, templates and snippets.</li><li>Finally BlogIt will create the demo blog resources.</li><p></p><p><b>Setup</b></p><p></p><p>BlogIt works best when you have <a href=\"https://rtfm.modx.com/revolution/2.x/administering-your-site/using-friendly-urls\" title=\"\" target=\"\">Friendly URL\'s active</a>.</p><p>To see the BlogIt options go to: \'Extras\' &gt; \'Configuration\', here you will find all the BlogIt options.</p><p></p><p><b></b></p><p><b>Support us</b></p><p>We spend a lot of time creating and maintaining this MODX Extra, please visit <a href=\"https://mpthemes.com/\" title=\"\" target=\"\">MPThemes.com</a> to find our premium MODX Revolution themes and support us. Or donate any amount when downloading BlogIt from <a href=\"https://blogit.mpthemes.com/\" title=\"\" target=\"\">blogit.mpthemes.com</a>.</p><p></p><p><b>Links</b></p><p></p><p>The official site for blog it is: <a href=\"https://blogit.mpthemes.com/\" title=\"\" target=\"\">blogit.mpthemes.com</a></p><p></p><p>For feature requests and bug submissions: <a href=\"https://github.com/DESIGNfromWITHIN/blogit/issues\" title=\"\" target=\"\">github.com/DESIGNfromWITHIN/blogit/issues</a></p><p></p>\";s:9:\"changelog\";s:470:\"<p>Changelog for blogit</p><p>blogit 1.2.0 (01-09-2016)</p><p>---------------------------------</p><p>- updated clientconfig, collections and tagger</p><p>- BlogIt site served over https now</p><p>- general cleanup&nbsp;</p><p>blogit 1.1.0 (02-09-2015)</p><p>---------------------------------</p><p>- add support for dependencies (need MODX 2.4.0-pl or up to use BlogIt)</p><p>blogit 1.0.0 (10-08-2015)</p><p>---------------------------------</p><p>- Initial Version</p>\";s:9:\"createdon\";s:24:\"2016-09-01T08:19:13+0000\";s:9:\"createdby\";s:16:\"DESIGNfromWITHIN\";s:8:\"editedon\";